{"tid":710850,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"以前讀到成隻狗咁，依家好後悔。","createTime":"2018-06-21T05:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T06:10:07.000Z","uid":164464,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a8cf00a288cda94b4c02cfee51e43b63438fa0bf","tid":710850,"uid":164464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"記得一年前放榜，自信爆棚嘅我平時死讀爛讀，諗住點都有20分夠入大學。<br />\n<br />\n點知，出到嚟得18分，反而隔離班個mk 仔有20分，夠入三大水泡科，我就只可以讀asso 。<br />\n<br />\n我一直都唔明，點解我一直咁比心機去讀書，功課交齊，返學上堂放學補習，都只可以做asshole 仔。但係個mk 仔又煙又酒，成日溝女屌西又曳都可以入u。<br />\n<br />\n早知當日我都唔讀書去玩 ，可能都仲有機會。<br />\n<br />\n今個sem gpa 唔過3...睇嚟又要讀多年..."},{"pid":"a99977dfe112a47fa6952af7afba36d4b30737eb","tid":710850,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:47:10.000Z","msg":"Asso...警犬毅進仔都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b548bb6a628aa7804673d08583d456103e1f4c0f","tid":710850,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"利：i大EE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaffa451f384e7a47e6f82eb5725fe4c06500258","tid":710850,"uid":121989,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"人地mk仔係平時唔讀書遮<br />\n但智商高你一大截<br />\n求其讀一讀就得<br />\n如果你學人地唔讀書<br />\nasso都冇得你讀"},{"pid":"f80eba08b13da655f05642bd8d512c5f471b596d","tid":710850,"uid":55386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"早d 接受 自己蠢呢個事實把啦"},{"pid":"153e8e880d3a2f281afdcfc3de7226d8505705e1","tid":710850,"uid":164464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要有得屌正妹"},{"pid":"a808b036fc3dfb0b1daecef2592010d051c61162","tid":710850,"uid":46433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"又loop？"}]}